```text
+-------------------+        +-------------------+
|     Digital      |--------|    Analog         |
|   Data / Signal  |        |   Carrier Wave   |
+-------------------+        +-------------------+
          ^                           ^
          |                           |
          v                           v
+-------------------+        +-------------------+
|   Modulation     |        | Demodulation      |
|   Techniques     |        | Techniques       |
+-------------------+        +-------------------+
```

